  "description": "Spouse/survivor auxiliary-benefit worked examples (42 USC 402(b)/(c)/(e)/(f)): our outputs vs SSA published figures, the policyengine-us PIA foundation cross-check, and the couple/survivor grid. Phase-C plumbing for #74 \u2014 reported, NOT gated.",
